Project Title: Fintech-Hackathon
Team Name: Pandas
Project Description: It is an intelligent dashboard for asset managers that transforms fragmented market news into actionable insights. Using AI-driven narrative detection, the platform tracks evolving macro themes, highlights “hot” developments, maps cross-market impacts, and generates risk implications for portfolios. The intuitive interface allows users to explore theme timelines, visualize causal chains, and access historical market memory—enabling faster, more informed decision-making in a high-volume, high-speed market environment.
